Interface SysMsgHooker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.sun.jna.AltCallingConvention, com.sun.jna.Library, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCall, com.sun.jna.win32.StdCallLibrary

    public interface SysMsgHooker
extends com.sun.jna.win32.StdCallLibrary
    An interface to SysMsgHooker.dll that contains callback functions like MouseProc, KeyboardProc, hooker setting functions and corresponding listener functions.
